'use client'; import React, { useEffect } from 'react'; function Team() { function loadBackgroudImages() { let backgroudImages = document.querySelectorAll('[data-background]'); if (backgroudImages.length > 0) { backgroudImages.forEach((element) => { let image = element.dataset.background; element.style.backgroundImage = `url('${image}')`; }); } } useEffect(() => { loadBackgroudImages(); }, []); return (
